### ===================================================================
### QALQON AI - NOTIFICATION (FCM) TEST (BOSQICH 7)
### ===================================================================

@token = SHU_YERGA_TOKEN_QOYASIZ
@fcmToken = SHU_YERGA_FCM_DEVICE_TOKEN

### ===================================================================
### 1-QADAM: LOGIN
### ===================================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: UZ

{
  "username": "uktamov9198@mail.ru",
  "password": "12345"
}

### ===================================================================
### 2-QADAM: FCM DEVICE TOKEN RO'YXATDAN O'TKAZISH
### Login muvaffaqiyatli bo'lgach token ni @token ga qo'ying
### ===================================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/device-token
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "token": "{{fcmToken}}",
  "platform": "ANDROID"
}

### ===================================================================
### 3-QADAM: LAWYER CHAT — PUSH TRIGGER (mijoz xabar yuboradi)
### Advokat qurilmasiga LAWYER_NEW_MESSAGE push kelishi kerak
### (firebase.enabled=true va haqiqiy FCM token bo'lsa)
### ===================================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats/start
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "lawyerId": 1,
  "message": {
    "content": "Assalomu alaykum, maslahat kerak."
  }
}

### ===================================================================
### 4-QADAM: FCM TOKEN O'CHIRISH (logout)
### ===================================================================
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/device-token?token={{fcmToken}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
